The paper proposes a novel method for multi-label node classification in attributed graphs using reinforcement learning. This work involves machine learning and artificial intelligence techniques, which are commonly associated with the cs.LG and cs.AI sub-categories. The proposed method also involves graph exploration and analysis, which falls under the cs.SI and cs.DS sub-categories. Finally, the paper deals with natural language processing tasks, such as text classification, which is related to the cs.CL sub-category.
